cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with natural language understanding and computer vision, which are both covered by the sub-categories cs.CL and cs.CV. The use of neural-based models suggests that the paper could also fit into the sub-categories cs.AI and cs.LG. Finally, the task of predicting spatial templates could be seen as a form of information retrieval, which is covered by the sub-category cs.IR.
